    "en": {
      "title": "America is ready to help Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is heartening that Sri Lanka has reached an interim agreement with the International Monetary Fund. In addition, US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sung said that the International Monetary Fund is the best tool to help Sri Lanka overcome the current economic crisis and represents the approaches and resources. The US is ready to continue to help Sri Lanka."
      ],
